@startuml 01-developer-onboarding

!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
title Flow 1: Developer Onboarding & SUI Deposit

actor "Developer" as Dev
participant "Platform\nBackend" as Backend
participant "Platform\nSmart Contract" as Contract
database "Sui\nBlockchain" as Sui

== Registration ==

Dev -> Backend: Register (email, project name)
Backend -> Backend: Create developer account
Backend -> Contract: Create DeveloperAccount object
Contract -> Sui: Store DeveloperAccount {\n  owner: dev_wallet,\n  balance: 0,\n  bandwidth_quota: 0,\n  bandwidth_used: 0\n}
Sui --> Contract: account_id
Contract --> Backend: account_id
Backend --> Dev: Account created\n+ platform API key

== Deposit SUI ==

Dev -> Contract: deposit(amount: 100 SUI)
Contract -> Contract: Validate sender == account owner
Contract -> Sui: Transfer SUI to contract
Contract -> Sui: Update DeveloperAccount {\n  balance += 100 SUI,\n  bandwidth_quota += calculated_gb\n}
Sui --> Contract: Success
Contract --> Dev: Deposit confirmed\nNew balance: 100 SUI\nBandwidth quota: X GB

note right of Contract
  Bandwidth quota calculated from SUI:
  e.g., 1 SUI = 10 GB bandwidth

  Storage is paid per-upload separately
end note

@enduml
